{"tid":1619744,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我宣布光復教成立","createTime":"2019-10-04T08:31:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T09:52:40.000Z","uid":242781,"like":33,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f6e31586375ad87792a954241b8c1406c957345f","tid":1619744,"uid":242781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:31:34.000Z","msg":"1. 基本宗旨：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港，時代革命</span><br />\n<br />\n2. 宗教活動：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不定期18區聚會</span><br />\n<br />\n3. 規條：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">出席宗教活動時必須<span style=\"color: red;\">蒙面</span></span><br />\n<br />\n4. 入教規則：<br />\n在心默念3次「光復香港，時代革命」，即屬教徒<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">「香港宗教與風俗相當多元化，根據《香港基本法》第 32 和 141 條，以及香港法例 383 章《香港人權法案條例》，信仰及宗教自由是香港居民享有的基本權利之一，並受法例保障。」</span><br />\n<br />\n你試下滅教，即刻全部宗教人士與你為敵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家快d入教<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a49b75f05dd86edb0242a9e82a118e1cc0e4713","tid":1619744,"uid":242781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:32:36.000Z","msg":"自推 1/100"},{"pid":"051dc867ac568d857b77cd7a07889b225a67ab33","tid":1619744,"uid":242781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:32:52.000Z","msg":"自推 2/100"},{"pid":"d4b2eb29ca844d316e0e450e8012e4611c24118b","tid":1619744,"uid":313172,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:35:59.000Z","msg":"焚我殘軀,熊熊聖火,<br />\n生亦何歡,死亦何苦? <br />\n為善除惡,唯光明故。 <br />\n喜樂悲愁,皆歸塵土。 <br />\n憐我世人,憂患實多!<br />\n<br />\n參見教主！光復香港 時代革命！"},{"pid":"2892370dbe51c4b40985c2b4c2e5c086687e2c23","tid":1619744,"uid":289034,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:36:50.000Z","msg":"我宣傳我正式加入光復教，<br />\n謹遵教條出街我會蒙面。<br />\n光服香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"43345435195a91130bc8324ca890ff16f658024e","tid":1619744,"uid":242781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04